{"text_id":178128,"tokens":["The"," advent"," of"," self","-","driving"," cars"," holds"," immense"," potential"," for"," revolution","izing"," the"," transportation"," industry"," and"," mitigating"," human"," errors"," that"," lead"," to"," accidents","."," However",","," this"," technological"," breakthrough"," also"," raises"," critical"," safety"," concerns"," that"," must"," be"," thoroughly"," examined","."," One"," of"," the"," primary"," worries"," is"," the"," potential"," for"," technological"," glitches"," and"," malfunctions"," in"," self","-","driving"," cars","."," Should"," the"," array"," of"," sensors"," and"," software"," that"," guide"," these"," vehicles"," encounter"," errors"," or"," inaccuracies",","," the"," consequences"," could"," be"," catastrophic","."," To"," address"," this",","," manufacturers"," of"," self","-","driving"," cars"," must"," prioritize"," rigorous"," testing"," and"," quality"," control"," to"," ensure"," that"," their"," vehicles"," operate"," reliably"," and"," safely"," on"," the"," road",".","\n\n","Another"," important"," consideration"," is"," how"," self","-","driving"," cars"," will"," respond"," in"," emergency"," situations",","," such"," as"," sudden"," medical"," emergencies"," or"," natural"," disasters","."," Driver","less"," vehicles"," may"," struggle"," to"," make"," life","-","or","-","death"," decisions",","," and"," their"," programming"," may"," not"," always"," be"," able"," to"," navigate"," such"," complexities","."," Moreover",","," there"," is"," the"," question"," of"," ethical"," considerations"," in"," these"," scenarios","."," Who"," or"," what"," entity"," should"," bear"," the"," responsibility"," if"," a"," self","-","driving"," car"," causes"," harm"," or"," fails"," to"," act"," appropriately"," in"," a"," high","-","risk"," situation","?"," Addressing"," these"," concerns"," through"," careful"," planning",","," policy"," development",","," and"," ethical"," frameworks"," is"," essential"," to"," ensure"," that"," self","-","driving"," cars"," do"," not"," exacerbate"," crises"," but"," rather"," contribute"," to"," safer"," and"," more"," effective"," emergency"," response"," measures",".","\n\n","In"," addition"," to"," safety"," concerns",","," the"," cost"," of"," maintenance"," and"," repairs"," for"," self","-","driving"," cars"," is"," an"," essential"," factor"," to"," consider","."," The"," complex"," technology"," involved"," in"," these"," vehicles"," will"," likely"," make"," repairs"," costly"," and"," difficult",","," which"," could"," pose"," a"," significant"," financial"," burden"," on"," consumers","."," This"," could"," lead"," to"," concerns"," about"," accessibility"," and"," equality",","," as"," not"," everyone"," would"," be"," able"," to"," afford"," the"," added"," costs"," of"," maintaining"," a"," self","-","driving"," car",".","\n\n","Considering"," these"," factors",","," while"," self","-","driving"," cars"," have"," the"," potential"," to"," transform"," transportation",","," there"," are"," valid"," concerns"," about"," their"," safety"," and"," practicality","."," Thorough"," testing",","," meticulous"," error"," handling",","," and"," thoughtful"," policies"," are"," necessary"," to"," ensure"," that"," we"," can"," reap"," the"," benefits"," of"," this"," technology"," while"," minimizing"," potential"," risks","."," Ultimately",","," despite"," the"," excitement"," surrounding"," driver","less"," cars",","," I"," believe"," that"," more"," advancements"," and"," improvements"," are"," needed"," to"," guarantee"," their"," reliability"," and"," affordability"," before"," I"," can"," wholeheartedly"," recommend"," them"," to"," others","."," ","\n\n","Would"," you"," like"," me"," to"," help"," you"," with"," any"," other"," problem"," statements","?"],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"cohere","label":1}